âš™ï¸ Setup Instructions
Requirements: Python 3.x

1.Clone or download the repo:
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/voting-app.git
cd voting-app


2.Install Flask if not already installed:

pip install flask


3.Initialize the database:

python init_db.py


4.Start the app:

python app.py
Open your browser and go to:

http://127.0.0.1:5000

ğŸ§ª SQL Injection Demo
Try submitting this as input in the voting form:

Candidate_id:
1', 1); UPDATE votes SET vote_count = 999 WHERE candidate_id = '1'; --

âœ… This injects a malicious SQL command that sets the vote count to 999 for candidate ID 1.


